n can  be  achieved  with  traditional  liposuction (with possibly enhanced results using laser-assisted liposuction)</mrk></g></seg-source><target><g id="660">  <mrk mtype="seg" mid="197"/></g></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="197"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">7v9rLdMkMbmjDIbyv28EG/LnaMqIGnarj22ddI2me+Y=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="119"/><sdl:cxt id="2"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="48243e2d-0783-42b6-a784-e7b00328fe50"><source><g id="663">More invasive and surgical  options  should al-ways be discussed with patients as more severe</g></source><seg-source><g id="663"><mrk mtype="seg" mid="198">More invasive and surgical  options  should al-ways be discussed with patients as more severe</mrk></g></seg-source><target><g id="663"><mrk mtype="seg" mid="198"/></g></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="198"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Egt4VcYJWaGjmMhXPdj3B8qrc4YPt9r9DGPJ5nXhCHE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="120"/><sdl:cxt id="2"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="49a83d2f-2bdb-4dd1-9843-808f156c3179"><source><g id="666">Downloaded for Anonymous User (n/a) at Seoul National University Hospital from ClinicalKey.com by Elsevier on July 27, 2023. For personal use only. No other uses without permission. Copyright ©2023. Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.</g><x id="667"/></source><seg-source><g id="666"><mrk mtype="seg" mid="199">Downloaded for Anonymous User (n/a) at Seoul National University Hospital from ClinicalKey.com by Elsevier on July 27, 2023.</mrk> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="200">For personal use only.</mrk> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="201">No other uses without permission.</mrk> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="202">Copyright ©2023.</mrk> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="203">Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.</mrk></g><x id="667"/></seg-source><target><g id="666"><mrk mtype="seg" mid="199"/> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="200"/> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="201"/> <mrk mtype="seg" mid="202"/